Note on dual licensing across the project:

This repository deliberately uses CC-BY-4.0 instead of MIT (used by sibling
code repos `fiscal-digital`, `fiscal-digital-web`, `fiscal-digital-collectors`)
because its content is primarily editorial and data-oriented (reports,
notebooks, exports), not software. This follows the Open Knowledge Foundation
convention for open data projects.

Software code that may exist alongside the data (utility scripts, notebook
helpers) is also covered by CC-BY-4.0 in this repository for consistency.
